-- Brazil's TIM Participacoes says Bradesco not studying Oi buy
-- By Alberto Alerigi
-- Wed Oct 08, 2014 08:54AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, Oct 8 (Reuters) - Brazilian telecommunications firm TIM Participacoes SA <TIMP3.SA> said in a securities filing on Wednesday it has hired Banco Bradesco <BBDC4.SA> to evaluate strategic alternatives.

